{"tid":1616603,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"禁蒙面法 唔等於 攬炒","createTime":"2019-10-03T13:12:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T14:38:14.000Z","uid":71060,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6b8a61978bfacf3327044cb1035c7132e3908a9d","tid":1616603,"uid":71060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:12:47.000Z","msg":"禁蒙面法 唔等於 攬炒<br />\n<br />\n禁蒙面法 (Anti-mask law) 係指係公眾集會例如示威遊行等戴面具或其他類似方式嚟遮掩身份<br />\n<br />\n唔係話你日常生活唔可以戴口罩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係話你唔可以因為宗教原因而蒙面呀<br />\n<br />\n就算加拿大美國德國都有相關法例，而且罰則都唔輕<br />\n<br />\n呢條提案係完全針對我哋手足呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但對其他人、商家佬、外資嚟講根本毫無影響<br />\n<br />\n咁點可以叫攬炒呀？各位手足唔好再話通過禁蒙面法齊攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f080380ee207b7f8a9faf5a08f8c6d3d56b7578e","tid":1616603,"uid":124252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:13:56.000Z","msg":"係唔係唔包popo?"},{"pid":"dc8930c79a80d7bfde9a8698676ac1ef2b69c129","tid":1616603,"uid":71060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f080380ee207b7f8a9faf5a08f8c6d3d56b7578e","tid":1616603,"uid":124252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:13:56.000Z","msg":"係唔係唔包popo?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:17:13.000Z","msg":"當然唔包啦，佢呢個法案嘅目的係為咗方便警察認人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"528b525e42d905ee1d3570b7298295bfe96adfa3","tid":1616603,"uid":71060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:17:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8525f2fc0757bf849194c44fcb5903e06407805","tid":1616603,"uid":71060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:17:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e27793e2e060ec9868a11d6044beb7df0a88a758","tid":1616603,"uid":71060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:17:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f22cf3c11bfd801cb158c13b60d1990dc4fc95fe","